<span class="postbody">Spirit Strike
<br />

<br />
1: Decrease Hit Points (HP) from 74 (L14) to 81 (L21)
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
Classes: Shm (L14), Bst (L30)
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
Skill: Evocation
<br />

<br />
Allowable Targets: All
<br />

<br />
Beneficial: Detrimental
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
Range to Target: 200 feet
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
Resistance Check: Cold
<br />

<br />
Base Fizzle : 25%
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
Mana Required: 75
<br />

<br />
Spell Duration: Instant
<br />

<br />
Casting Time: 2.45 seconds
<br />

<br />
Spell Recovery: 2.50 seconds
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
<br />

<br />
Spell cast on you: You stagger as spirits of frost slam against you.
<br />

<br />
Spell cast on someone: An orc centurion staggers as spirits of frost slam against them.
<br />

<br />

<br />

<br />
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------- <B>
<br />
Frued NoEinstein
<br />

<br />
Corpse for Rallos Zek
<br />

<br />
Undead Member of Tranquil Domain
<br />

<br />
Ogre Reaver</B><i></i></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
